Results Summary: OTA Efficiency Study Objective - Measure impact of OTA delta updates vs full-image updates  Findings - Delta updates reduced payload by 62% and cut maintenance windows by 35% in stage
dows by 35% in staged deployments  Constraints - Delta generation less effective when base firmware deviates >2 versions; recommend aligned baselines.
